{"title":"Hexo Blog 使用指南","uid":"dfe23e87b39ae11339911ece4bdb4cea","slug":"Hexo Blog 使用指南","date":"2023-11-14T23:59:59.000Z","updated":"2023-11-14T17:51:58.000Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Hexo Blog 使用指南.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Wu-yikun/OSS/PicGo/202310142119069.jpg","content":"<h2 id=\"Hexo-常用指令\"><a href=\"#Hexo-常用指令\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Hexo 常用指令\"></a>Hexo 常用指令</h2><div class=\"language-bash\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">bash</span><pre class=\"shiki material-theme-palenight\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #676E95; font-style: italic\"># 启动本地服务器</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #FFCB6B\">$</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">hexo</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">s</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #676E95; font-style: italic\"># 清理缓存文件</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #FFCB6B\">$</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">hexo</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">clean</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #676E95; font-style: italic\"># 生成静态文件 public/</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #FFCB6B\">$</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">hexo</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">g</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #676E95; font-style: italic\"># 部署网站</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #FFCB6B\">$</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">hexo</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">d</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #676E95; font-style: italic\"># 新建文章 _posts/</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #FFCB6B\">$</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">hexo</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">new</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> [layout] </span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">&lt;title&gt;</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&quot;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #676E95; font-style: italic\"># 新建页面 source/xxx/index.md</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #FFCB6B\">$</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">hexo</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">new</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">page</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">&lt;page&gt;</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&quot;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #676E95; font-style: italic\"># 新建草稿 _drafts/</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #FFCB6B\">$</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">hexo</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">new</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">draft</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">&lt;title&gt;</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&quot;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #676E95; font-style: italic\"># 发布草稿 _drafts/ -&gt; _posts/</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #FFCB6B\">$</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">hexo</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">publish</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">draft</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&quot;&quot;</span></span></code></pre></div><h2 id=\"自动化部署\"><a href=\"#自动化部署\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"自动化部署\"></a>自动化部署</h2><blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>可以参考「<a href=\"https://lhcfl.github.io/2023/09/24/%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AEHexo%E7%9A%84%E8%87%AA%E5%8A%A8%E6%8E%A8%E9%80%81/\">配置 Hexo 的自动推送</a>」</p>\n<p>也可以参考官方方法：<a href=\"https://hexo.io/zh-cn/docs/github-pages.html\">在 GitHub Pages 上部署 Hexo</a></p></blockquote>\n<p>还在用 <code>hexo d</code> 来推送你的 Blog 到 GitHub 上吗？应该使用 Github Actions 自动推送！具体细节参考文章！</p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>当每次要删除文章时（**新建文章同理，但最好使用 <code>hexo new &quot;title&quot;</code><em><em>），直接把文章从 📂</em>_post</em> 文件夹中删除，再执行 <code>add</code>、<code>commit</code>、<code>push</code> 三连 <strong>source repo</strong>，会自动触发 <strong>Action</strong> 部署 <em>public</em> 文件夹到 <strong>target repo</strong> !</p>\n<p><strong>强烈建议</strong>：❌不要使用 hexo 自带的命令进行手动部署！</p></blockquote>\n<ul>\n<li><input checked=\"\" disabled=\"\" type=\"checkbox\"> source repo: <a href=\"https://github.com/Wu-yikun/wu-yikun.github.io-source\">https://github.com/Wu-yikun/wu-yikun.github.io-source</a></li>\n<li><input checked=\"\" disabled=\"\" type=\"checkbox\"> target repo: <a href=\"https://github.com/Wu-yikun/wu-yikun.github.io\">https://github.com/Wu-yikun/wu-yikun.github.io</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Wu-yikun/OSS/PicGo/202311131644584.png\"></p>\n","text":"Hexo 常用指令bash# 启动本地服务器 $ hexo s # 清理缓存文件 $ hexo clean # 生成静态文件 public/ $ hexo g ...","permalink":"/post/Hexo Blog 使用指南","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":813,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"Blog","slug":"Blog","count":3,"path":"api/categories/Blog.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"hexo","slug":"hexo","count":1,"path":"api/tags/hexo.json"},{"name":"博客","slug":"博客","count":3,"path":"api/tags/博客.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Hexo-%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E6%8C%87%E4%BB%A4\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Hexo 常用指令</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E8%87%AA%E5%8A%A8%E5%8C%96%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2\"><span class=\"toc-text\">自动化部署</span></a></li></ol>","author":{"name":"Wu-Yikun","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Wu-yikun/